---
  <section
    id="brand-intro"
    class="grid items-start gap-10 bg-cream px-5 py-20 md:gap-20 md:px-10 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] lg:gap-20 lg:px-20 lg:py-[110px]"
  >
    <div class="intro-left">
      <div
        class="mb-5 flex items-center gap-3 font-body text-[10px] tracking-[0.35em] text-dark-red uppercase"
      >
        <span class="block h-px w-7 bg-dark-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        Our Story
      </div>
      <h2
        class="font-serif text-[clamp(34px,4vw,52px)] font-light leading-tight text-dark-brown"
      >
        Crafting <em class="italic text-dark-red">Unforgettable</em><br />Culinary Experiences
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div class="intro-right pt-0 md:pt-[18px]">
      <p class="mb-6 font-body text-[19px] leading-[1.85] text-[var(--text-muted-on-cream)]">
        Elamrit was born from a belief that food is more than sustenance — it is ceremony. Every plate we present
        carries the weight of occasion, the warmth of tradition, and the precision of craft. From intimate private
        dinners to grand destination weddings spanning across India, we bring the same obsessive attention to flavour,
        presentation, and service.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6 font-body text-[19px] leading-[1.85] text-[var(--text-muted-on-cream)]">
        Rooted in Pune and catering Pan India, Elamrit blends the richness of Indian culinary heritage with a modern,
        elevated aesthetic — creating experiences that linger long after the last bite.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-[52px] grid grid-cols-1 gap-px bg-[rgba(81,3,12,0.08)] sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-dark-red bg-cream px-7 py-8">
          <div class="font-display text-[38px] leading-none tracking-wide text-dark-red">500+</div>
          <div class="mt-2 font-body text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] text-dark-red uppercase">Events Crafted</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-dark-red bg-cream px-7 py-8">
          <div class="font-display text-[38px] leading-none tracking-wide text-dark-red">12+</div>
          <div class="mt-2 font-body text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] text-dark-red uppercase">Cities Served</div>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t-[3px] border-dark-red bg-cream px-7 py-8">
          <div class="font-display text-[38px] leading-none tracking-wide text-dark-red">98%</div>
          <div class="mt-2 font-body text-[11px] tracking-[0.2em] text-dark-red uppercase">Client Delight</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
